{"tid":138461,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"點解決隻貓日日想出街既問題?","createTime":"2017-02-28T15:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T05:54:55.000Z","uid":54740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cef2ae5139fc344da8b747dd5bedef462b72035c","tid":138461,"uid":54740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:09:10.000Z","msg":"屋企早排養左隻流浪貓,<br />\n平時都係餵下佢食野,比張床佢訓就算,<br />\n跟住佢中意訓覺就訓覺出街就出街(住村屋)。<br />\n<br />\n上星期貓貓後腳受傷,谷膿,最後去左睇獸醫。<br />\n好似係因為隻腳唔知吉到乜野所以受傷<br />\n<br />\n係一個好心又養貓經驗豐富既鄰居既悉心照顧之下,宜家已經好返,<br />\n但鄰居就叫我地唔好再比佢出街,唔係一陣又受傷又要睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n本來我地都好贊成唔比佢出街, 但係佢日喵夜又喵,成日都想搵方法出街<br />\n所以想請問...有咩方法可以令佢乖乖留係屋企?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩一個唔留神,開一開門,隻貓又出左街,宜家係出面車底溝緊女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f003e81701a80c58bf3bd51930a4b98be87b450e","tid":138461,"uid":18491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:11:07.000Z","msg":"幫佢絕育"},{"pid":"b67532fa847a70e5973188c913e3ca7e50bc621e","tid":138461,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:11:27.000Z","msg":"養多隻 等佢日日留係屋企扑野<br />\nBtw閹左未"},{"pid":"447c57d72d865179e10b62b1082399b24057fa16","tid":138461,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:11:50.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"80c678ed20ae0ed0ce64aabcf0d7d276f0dc5fab","tid":138461,"uid":54740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:12:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫佢絕育</blockquote><br />\n第一次見佢果陣已經絕左育"},{"pid":"b04859aada813a2f7c0535c15b9b4135e656f369","tid":138461,"uid":5937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:12:44.000Z","msg":"我隻貓之前都係流浪貓 你一接流浪貓返屋企點都要困返一排籠等佢個性唔好再咁野 比佢習慣下唔再流離浪盪"},{"pid":"5b0f84da594fb6e2488c96342758bf95100f39c4","tid":138461,"uid":54740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:13:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>養多隻 等佢日日留係屋企扑野<br />\nBtw閹左未</blockquote><br />\n我地都想收養埋佢條女,但奈何果隻貓女實在係太驚人,<br />\n即使我地比佢訓比野仍食,佢都仲係好驚我地"},{"pid":"9d3f8be1063c485e961638532af154edddd977bb","tid":138461,"uid":53434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:14:45.000Z","msg":"純文字討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屋企整d 高台，貓樹俾佢玩，等佢分散下注意力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf7736b82a450ed2d0ee421d842c29830becf1a","tid":138461,"uid":54740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:16:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隻貓之前都係流浪貓 你一接流浪貓返屋企點都要困返一排籠等佢個性唔好再咁野 比佢習慣下唔再流離浪盪</blockquote><br />\n諗緊聽日買條貓繩綁住佢唔比佢走...<br />\n<br />\n如果佢肯返黎既話"},{"pid":"b46384680c19587ea18f20e90d5e7e76b18700f9","tid":138461,"uid":54740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:17:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>純文字討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屋企整d 高台，貓樹俾佢玩，等佢分散下注意力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢返左黎先影啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屋企無咩位方貓樹高台, 諗緊買D貓玩具比佢玩"},{"pid":"2164c3bdc9176d425eead0e4ff05f3cd4cb9c2bf","tid":138461,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:27:40.000Z","msg":"首先要提供圖片同影片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc6fc4c043d654b7cb53e28e718039367f92672","tid":138461,"uid":54740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4pwko28e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4pwko28e&h=2abac3dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩返左黎<br />\n黃色果隻係養開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白色果隻黎混吉既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df49c2c96f9c6856e3db844b02061ed63418e872","tid":138461,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/4pwko28e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4pwko28e&h=2abac3dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩返左黎<br />\n黃色果隻係養開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白色果隻黎混吉既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 帶女返來開p"},{"pid":"ae607ab35da2f048287aace5cf5a35217f789abf","tid":138461,"uid":4589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:53:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/4pwko28e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4pwko28e&h=2abac3dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩返左黎<br />\n黃色果隻係養開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白色果隻黎混吉既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 帶女返來開p</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n養埋白色個隻囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f6c92e03397d61e3869d6b03ddb6e9fbc69a64","tid":138461,"uid":4589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:58:12.000Z","msg":"佢喵咪唔好理佢<br />\nor 同佢玩 分散佢注意力<br />\n放哂佢d 電<br />\n佢應該會去訓覺<br />\n<br />\n重覆幾日應該ok<br />\n如果屋企放唔到貓樹<br />\n睇下有冇機會用傢俬整到高低落差<br />\n比佢係最高位坐or瞓 增加安全感<br />\nor 係食飯枱放d 細既貓樹加貓窩<br />\n<br />\n再唔係係窗口放吊床比佢哂太陽<br />\n<br />\n祝樓主好運"},{"pid":"bb950fcf22845495a13acdedf1fb4bb526998e55","tid":138461,"uid":5937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:03:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我隻貓之前都係流浪貓 你一接流浪貓返屋企點都要困返一排籠等佢個性唔好再咁野 比佢習慣下唔再流離浪盪</blockquote><br />\n諗緊聽日買條貓繩綁住佢唔比佢走...<br />\n<br />\n如果佢肯返黎既話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實正常養就一定係會鎖好門窗 裝晒紗窗唔比佢走到出去<br />\n你無可能期望佢會聽聽話話 你話唔出就唔出咁<br />\n喺屋企嗰陣多啲同佢玩 陪佢多啲 啱啱養就實要困籠<br />\n你唔想佢出去走嚟走去整親 就唯有自己諗呢啲方法<br />\n無得意旨隻貓自動波"},{"pid":"aaca568df6e7703ab5fc0eb398ca166585c60ada","tid":138461,"uid":54740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:04:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/4pwko28e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4pwko28e&h=2abac3dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩返左黎<br />\n黃色果隻係養開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白色果隻黎混吉既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 帶女返來開p</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n養埋白色個隻囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n白色太驚人..養唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽日準備買條貓繩同整個可開關既貓網"},{"pid":"fcc940768927f9c7c23e69e32532baadbca4ab61","tid":138461,"uid":18048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:07:40.000Z","msg":"大家坐低傾下"},{"pid":"4fcf6465a83370e5018592d370cbd69b53faa00f","tid":138461,"uid":4589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:12:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/4pwko28e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4pwko28e&h=2abac3dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩返左黎<br />\n黃色果隻係養開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白色果隻黎混吉既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 帶女返來開p</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n養埋白色個隻囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n白色太驚人..養唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽日準備買條貓繩同整個可開關既貓網</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你一係困房<br />\n唔好用貓繩啦"},{"pid":"92876853d7ca139c895761eb9e3d2c55802d610f","tid":138461,"uid":4589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:13:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/4pwko28e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4pwko28e&h=2abac3dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩返左黎<br />\n黃色果隻係養開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白色果隻黎混吉既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 帶女返來開p</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n養埋白色個隻囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n白色太驚人..養唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽日準備買條貓繩同整個可開關既貓網</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你一係唔好比白色個隻出返去流浪<br />\n我覺得你隻黃色貓出去原因都係搵白色貓"},{"pid":"686a5eaf16bbb77109743f5f0694b79b3d0a8f99","tid":138461,"uid":54740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:25:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n你一係困房<br />\n唔好用貓繩啦</blockquote><br />\n我屋企房門無得鎖..隻貓識得自己開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c20c0eaf6bf30e53b2f9080843540fc906a8cc","tid":138461,"uid":54740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:32:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n咁你一係唔好比白色個隻出返去流浪<br />\n我覺得你隻黃色貓出去原因都係搵白色貓</blockquote><br />\n呢個真..但隻白貓唔肯住入黎"},{"pid":"8b5e8733a209d8ff2630aa30e7f60402d7731ee0","tid":138461,"uid":87788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T23:23:37.000Z","msg":"我自己隻由細養到大嘅家貓都係每日要落樓下玩，好在住村屋有花園仔比佢行下。你係擔心嘅不如用貓帶以散步形式同佢每日都行一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91b86aa10695b44cf907368039ae7fc0c14db11","tid":138461,"uid":4589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:00:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己隻由細養到大嘅家貓都係每日要落樓下玩，好在住村屋有花園仔比佢行下。你係擔心嘅不如用貓帶以散步形式同佢每日都行一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讚成a 位巴打既講法"},{"pid":"9b0bd70b5e82fe0d64d2a08a395047a2cc12626c","tid":138461,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:54:55.000Z","msg":"養動物好唔人道就係咁解<br />\n困係屋企 不如去死<br />\n貓仔想出去玩咪由佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}